c) Using the NVIDIA Dataset ONLY for permitted purposes under NVIDIA's license

NVIDIA Dataset License Agreement is available at:
https://huggingface.co/datasets/nvidia/PhysicalAI-Autonomous-Vehicles-NuRec

You acknowledge that:
